'''犹太保卫同盟'''（Jewish Defense League，縮寫JDL），是一個[[猶太|猶太]][[極右派|極右派]]宗教政治激進組織，其宣稱的目標是“用一切必要手段保護猶太人以免於受到[[反猶太主義|反猶太主義]]的威脅”。<ref name="backgrounder">{{cite web|url=http://www.adl.org/extremism/jdl_chron.asp|title=Anti-Defamation League on JDL|publisher=Adl.org|accessdate=2011-11-23|archive-date=2010-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100414090038/http://www.adl.org/extremism/jdl_chron.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖然該集團聲稱，它“毫不含糊地譴責[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]”，並指出，它有一個“決不容忍的政策以對抗恐怖主義和其他重罪的行為”，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jdl.org/index.php/ideology-advocacy/anti-terrorism-racism/ |title=Anti-Terrorism & Anti-Racism | Jewish Defense League |publisher=Jdl.org |date=2009-07-30 |accessdate=2011-11-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321025440/http://jdl.org/index.php/ideology-advocacy/anti-terrorism-racism/ |archivedate=2012-03-21 }}</ref>它仍在2001年[[美國聯邦調查局|美國聯邦調查局]]歸類為“右翼恐怖組織”。<ref name=fbi>{{cite web|url=http://www.fbi.gov/stats-services/publications/terror/terrorism-2000-2001/?searchterm=JDL|title=FBI — Terrorism 2000/2001|publisher=Fbi.gov|accessdate=2011-11-23|archive-date=2016-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160605122106/https://www.fbi.gov/stats-services/publications/terror/terrorism-2000-2001/?searchterm=JDL|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=spl>{{Cite web |url=http://www.splcenter.org/intel/intelreport/article.jsp?aid=123 |title=SPLCenter.org: Anti-Arab Terrorism<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-09-15 |archive-date=2014-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141029232940/http://www.splcenter.org/intel/intelreport/article.jsp?aid=123 |dead-url=no }}</ref>根據聯邦調查局的資料，JDL一直參與策劃及執行在美國的恐怖行動。<ref name=fbi />

該組織由{{link-en|梅爾·卡漢|Meir Kahane}}於1968年在[[紐約市|紐約市]]創立，宣稱其目的是在當地反猶太主義氛圍下保護猶太人。<ref name="backgrounder" /><ref name="MIPT">[http://www.start.umd.edu/start/data/tops/terrorist_organization_profile.asp?id=183 JDL group profile from ''National Consortium for the Study of Terror and Responses to Terrorism''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100828165700/http://www.start.umd.edu/start/data/tops/terrorist_organization_profile.asp?id=183 |date=2010-08-28 }}</ref>他們批判蘇聯，因而贏得支持，從“治安維持會”而逐漸轉型成為一個號稱會員數多達15,000人的組織。<ref name=hewitt>{{cite book|title=Understanding Terrorism in America: From the Klan to Al Qaeda|first=Christopher|last=Hewitt|pages=35f|year=2002|publisher=Routledge|isbn=0-415-27765-5}}</ref>他們對美國的阿拉伯及蘇聯財產發動炸彈攻擊，<ref>Hewitt, p. 65</ref>對各種所謂的“猶太人的敵人”進行暗殺，從阿拉伯裔美國人政治活動家到新納粹分子都成為其目標。<ref>Nasseph McCarus, Ernest. ''The Development of Arab-American Identity''. 1994, pp. 180–3</ref>一些JDL成員涉及在美國和其他國家的暴力甚至是致命的攻擊，包括1985年美國－阿拉伯反歧視委員會地區主任亞歷克斯·奧德赫謀殺案、1994年的[[易卜拉欣大慘案|易卜拉欣大慘案]]和2001年刺殺美國國會議員達雷爾·伊薩的計畫。<ref>Kushner, Harvey W. ''Encyclopedia of Terrorism''. 2003, pp. 192–3</ref>國家預防恐怖主義紀念研究所
是由[[美國國土安全部|美國國土安全部]]資助的合約承包商及顧問公司，在其建立的恐怖主義數據庫中，JDL被標識為“前恐怖組織。”<ref>[http://www.tkb.org/Group.jsp?groupID=183 MIPT Terrorism Knowledge Base] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090921192226/http://www.tkb.org/Group.jsp?groupID=183 |date=2009-09-21 }}</ref> 而JDL的網站上則說，它反對恐怖主義。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jdl.org/ |title=The Official Jewish Defense League Website |publisher=Jdl.org |accessdate=2011-11-23 |archive-date=2012-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120904124803/http://www.jdl.org/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1994年，JDL的姐妹運動[[凱煦|凱煦及卡漢永生]]均被視為恐怖組織而禁止在以色列境內活動，基於威脅到國家安全的理由。<ref name=terror>{{cite web |last=Levinson |first=Chaim |url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/french-branch-of-jewish-terror-group-coming-to-israel-to-defend-settlements-1.384723 |title=French branch of Jewish terror group coming to Israel 'to defend settlements' - Israel News | Haaretz Daily Newspaper |publisher=Haaretz.com |date=2011-09-16 |accessdate=2013-08-14 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924221644/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/news/french-branch-of-jewish-terror-group-coming-to-israel-to-defend-settlements-1.384723 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他們在美國和歐盟也遭到禁止。 “JDL加拿大”仍然是合法的，<ref name=Rabble>{{cite web|last=Lehrer|first=Andy|title=Hypocrisy in Action: The JDL and the Galloway ban|url=http://rabble.ca/news/whos-terrorist-jdl-and-galloway-ban|work=Rabble|accessdate=8 February 2014|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226105907/https://rabble.ca/news/whos-terrorist-jdl-and-galloway-ban|dead-url=no}}</ref>儘管它與被禁組織具有相同的思想、目標和標識。<ref name=JDL_Canada>{{cite web|title=About Us|url=http://jdl-canada.com/about-us/|work=JDL Canada|accessdate=8 February 2014|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309221440/http://www.jdl-canada.com/about-us/|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，JDL在法國分支機構則是非法的。<ref name="Ahren">{{cite web |last=Ahren |first=Raphael |url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/french-arab-recovering-after-revenge-attack-by-jews/ |title=French Arab recovering after 'revenge attack' by Jews |publisher=The Times of Israel |date=2013-06-05 |accessdate=2013-08-14 |archive-date=2013-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130811041151/http://www.timesofisrael.com/french-arab-recovering-after-revenge-attack-by-jews/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>好幾位JDL成員和領導者死於非命，包括卡漢本身。<ref name=deaths>{{cite web |last=Berman |first=Lazar |url=http://www.timesofisrael.com/jdl-vice-chairmans-suicide-continues-chain-of-violent-deaths/ |title=JDL vice chairman’s suicide continues chain of violent deaths |publisher=The Times of Israel |date=2012-08-17 |accessdate=2013-08-14 |archive-date=2013-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131011030033/http://www.timesofisrael.com/jdl-vice-chairmans-suicide-continues-chain-of-violent-deaths/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

